name: LORE CARD 002: The Gangs
description: Life on a new world can be harsh. As a result, many people have fallen into gangs to survive. The Staggrasp Scrappers, The Bookbringers, Mapleborough Royales & the Hover Girls (who call themselves ‘The Starfalls’) are just a few of many with their own distinct identity and turf.   With a dark future and an overwhelming sense of impotence a lot of the colony's young members choose to live fast and die young.  Engaging in daring activities and pursuing a hedonistic and wild lifestyle, they’ll put it all on the line for a bit of coin and to protect their own.
